---
title: Bacon, Leek and Mushroom Pie with Mustard and Mashed Potato Top
description: This Bacon, Leek and Mushroom Pie is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
